LMFS PCM Player based on PulseAudio demo program

You should run the build_<your_platform>.sh to build the binary file
Dependences: libpulse-dev libmagic-dev
usage:
    Rename the root to source code directory to "player"
    Import(don't start python under the source code directory):
    >>> import player
    >>> player.play(["example.wav", "example1.wav"])
    >>> player.stopById(0)
    >>> player.bgm("test.wav")
    >>> player.stopById(0)
